## Quick start

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r meomaya/requirements.txt
```

Run API:

```bash
uvicorn meomaya.api.server:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000
```

Run CLI:

```bash
python -m meomaya "Hello from MeoMaya!" --mode text
```

Offline mode:

```bash
export MEOMAYA_STRICT_OFFLINE=1
```

